    <item>
      <title>数千人在拉巴特游行，要求结束摩洛哥与以色列的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/thousands-march-rabat-demanding-end-morocco-israel-ties-2023-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，数千名抗议者在拉巴特举行了自加沙战争爆发以来最大规模的亲巴勒斯坦游行之一，要求结束摩洛哥与以色列的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/thousands-march-rabat-demanding-end-morocco-israel-ties-2023-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 13:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地区紧张局势加剧，伊朗海军接收新型巡航导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-navy-receives-new-cruise-missiles-amid-growing-regional-tension-2023-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体周日报道，伊朗海军已接收射程 1,000 公里（621 英里）的巡航导弹和侦察直升机，美国指责伊朗对印度洋的一艘化学油轮发动无人机袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-navy-receives-new-cruise-missiles-amid-growing-regional-tension-2023-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 11:37:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦亲欧洲总统桑杜表示将寻求连任</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/moldovas-pro-european-president-sandu-says-she-will-seek-second-term-2023-12-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛雅·桑杜谴责俄罗斯入侵乌克兰，并指责莫斯科密谋政变推翻她。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/moldovas-pro-european-president-sandu-says-she-will-seek-second-term-2023-12-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
